1
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:05,880
I believe

2
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,000
the Duke is still alive.

3
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,440
Still alive.

4
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,730
It's exactly as the Empress Dowager said.

5
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,760
Unable to live,

6
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,400
and unable to die.

7
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,680
Qingshu.

8
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,720
Even if I have to search the four seas,

9
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:36,479
and travel across the nine provinces,

10
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:37,400
I will bring my father-in-law

11
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,039
back to you safely.

12
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,920
Nonsense.

13
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,890
Who is your father-in-law?

14
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,680
I was wrong.

15
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,450
I deserve a beating.

16
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,570
Second Miss Yan,

17
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,980
I trust you have been well.

18
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,210
Second Miss Yan,

19
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,520
you should know

20
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,280
that Beidi does business

21
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,240
based on sincerity,

22
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,900
not the person.

23
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,620
The map to Yaowang Valley.

24
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,900
I heard Yaowang Valley

25
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,040
is full of rare and precious medicinal herbs,

26
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:28,560
including life-saving lingzhi that money can't buy.

27
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,440
This map,

28
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,760
where did you get it?

29
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:32,200
By killing and robbing.

30
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:36,620
Yan Qingshu has the map of the Heishui Valley iron mine.

31
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,200
After it's done,

32
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,960
you will get an iron mountain.

33
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,040
This is my

34
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,820
greatest sincerity to Beidi.

35
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,120
Good.

36
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,200
Beidi gets the iron mountain,

37
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:50,200
and Second Miss Yan gets the person.

38
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,360
Deal.

39
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:03,650
Your Majesty, Cui Linlang has been brought here.

40
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,880
Why don't you kneel before me?

41
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,980
Cui Linlang, daughter of a guilty minister,

42
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,089
pays respects to Your Majesty.

43
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,040
Since you like this posture,

44
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,170
then stay kneeling.

45
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:27,090
I seek an audience late at night

46
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:30,820
because I have a secret letter for Your Majesty to read.

47
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,520
The princess seeks an audience tonight

48
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,360
to tell me a ghost story.

49
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,320
I am not good at telling stories.

50
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,730
I only have one request.

51
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,920
To beg me

52
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,200
to execute your entire Cui family?

53
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,720
I implore Your Majesty

54
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:27,650
to arrange my marriage to the heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei,

55
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,200
Xiao Jingyan.

56
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,159
A daughter of a guilty family

57
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,840
dares to cling to the heir.

58
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,640
I am willing to help Your Majesty

59
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,200
get rid of Xiao Jingyan.

60
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,920
I am the Emperor.

61
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:43,620
Why would I need to borrow your knife to kill?

62
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:48,760
Regarding the past matters between Your Majesty and my father,

63
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,760
I

64
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,280
know a thing or two.

65
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,300
The Northern border deployment map.

66
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:09,320
The Western Region wine bestowed by the Emperor yesterday

67
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,520
was poisoned, right?

68
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,720
Someone from Zichen Hall sneaked into the mansion and did it.

69
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:16,120
This person is the Emperor's trusted aide.

70
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,720
That dog Emperor

71
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,080
wants to get rid of me now that I've outlived my usefulness.

72
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,320
Since the Emperor has no regard for our past friendship,

73
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:25,480
don't blame me for turning ruthless.

74
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:26,800
Who is it?

75
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,040
The Princess is deeply in love,

76
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,700
but Prince Xiao shows no pity.

77
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,640
I am willing to grant your wish.

78
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,370
Tomorrow, I will issue a decree

79
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,760
to arrange a marriage for you two.

80
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:43,420
Thank you for your immense grace, Your Majesty.

81
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:47,040
When I am buried in the same grave as Prince Xiao,

82
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,720
the past matters between Your Majesty and my father

83
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:53,520
will be sealed forever.

84
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,560
Qingshu.

85
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,120
Wait for me.

86
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,560
I will definitely marry you.

87
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,520
Brother Yuheng.

88
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,120
Even in your dreams,

89
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,580
you are calling out my sister's name.

90
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:44,840
What a pity.

91
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:49,060
My sister won't live to see the day you marry her.

92
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:02,020
I had them buy your favorite flower cake.

93
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,640
We'll eat it when we get back.

94
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,890
Are you okay?

95
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,600
I'm fine.

96
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,400
Stay here and wait for me.

97
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,610
Take them alive.

98
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,080
Qingshu.

99
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,040
Mother.

100
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,340
You shouldn't be here.

101
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,040
Go find your father.

102
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,720
Mother.

103
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,000
Qingshu.

104
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,200
Come to me.

105
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,120
Father.

106
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:57,240
Father.

107
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,120
Qingshu.

108
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:00,520
Run.

109
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,040
Father.

110
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,320
Qingshu.

111
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,640
Wake up, Qingshu.

112
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,920
Qingshu, wake up.

113
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,680
Qingshu, wake up.

114
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,160
Qingshu.

115
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,370
Are you okay?

116
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:50,600
I'm fine.

117
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:54,890
Look at this.

118
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,170
The Beidi people

119
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:11,650
want me to bring the Heishuigu iron mine map in person

120
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,540
in exchange for my father's life.

121
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,680
My father is still alive.

122
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,640
He is in Beidi.

123
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:27,890
You're injured.

124
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,520
I'm fine.

125
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,560
Let me see.

126
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:37,640
It's just a scratch.

127
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:40,780
It's poisoned.

128
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,280
Xiao Jingyan.

129
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:49,600
Xiao Jingyan!

130
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,010
Are you alright?

131
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:58,680
Here.

132
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,600
Drink up.

133
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:07,640
Did you know that

134
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,490
Beidi's Wolf Flower poison

135
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,880
is truly deadly?

136
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,800
If I hadn't made the antidote in time,

137
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:14,240
You...

138
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:17,280
you would have gone to the netherworld.

139
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,090
What are you smiling at?

140
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,940
Miss Qingshu, for saving my life,

141
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,540
I will remember it.

142
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,240
I have nothing to repay you with.

143
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,040
Then you should think carefully

144
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,240
about how to repay me.

145
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:43,360
Then I can only

146
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,540
give myself to you.

147
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:57,120
Your Highness, Attendant Liu has arrived.

148
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,320
Attendant Liu.

149
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,280
By the grace of Heaven,

150
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:06,280
the Emperor decrees:

151
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:09,340
Qingshu, the eldest daughter of the Yan family,

152
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,240
possesses great wisdom

153
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,620
and exceptional determination.

154
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,360
She is suited for the inner court

155
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,000
and is hereby granted an imperial title.

156
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,960
The Luantai shall prepare the ceremony

157
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:21,600
and choose an auspicious day for the Six Rites.

158
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,960
May this union be harmonious,

159
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,040
and bring eternal glory to the palace.

160
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,520
Respect this.

161
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:43,880
Heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei, hear the decree.

162
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:55,640
By the grace of Heaven,

163
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,360
the Emperor decrees:

164
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:56,480
the Emperor decrees:

165
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,840
the Emperor decrees:

166
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,980
The heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei

167
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:02,620
wields a golden halberd to defend the state.

168
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,680
The solitary phoenix of the Cui family

169
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:07,280
receives the jade dew and nurtures pure grace.

170
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,720
Today, by imperial edict,

171
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,200
we bind you in a century of marriage.

172
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:15,960
May you follow the rites of Zhou with geese as gifts,

173
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:18,960
and emulate Bao and Huan in harmony.

174
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,280
From now on,

175
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:22,280
may auspiciousness abide,

176
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:25,520
and the northern frontier remain as firm as a rock forever.

177
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,960
Respect this.

178
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:32,280
Please receive the decree.

179
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,360
Cuimei.

180
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,240
Yong.

181
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:14,960
Huachao.

182
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:15,960
Weikun, Huachao.

183
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,840
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

184
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:22,560
Shuang,

185
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,200
Shuang,

186
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:24,160
Ningzheng.

187
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:27,840
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

188
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,040
Weichao.

189
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,320
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

190
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:50,760
Xi,

191
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:52,320
Xi,

192
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:52,800
Xi,

193
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:53,440
Tao, Qiang.

194
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,100
Tao, Qiang.

195
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,200
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

196
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:03,200
Yiyi.

197
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:10,600
Si.
